column5: Has anybody been to this outpost? I will be going in September and am very excited. Would like some info on what to expect so I can plan.JohnL
thought I'd bring it to the top once more.Has no one heard of this lake?

My Brother fished out of a Rusty Myer camp several years ago and said it was first class and the fishing was good to real good. I dont know what lake he fished but I bet you will do well and have a great time....Good Luck
